sp;\u2013 technical assistance\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! Chart (1994)\n! Position\n|-\n|align=\"left\"| Australian [[ARIA Charts|ARIA Albums Chart]]<ref>\"[http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=R.E.M.&titel=Monster&cat=a R.E.M. - Monster (Album)] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110823161445/http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=R.E.M.&titel=Monster&cat=a |date=August 23, 2011 }}\". Australian-charts.com. Retrieved on March 19, 2009.</ref>\n| 2\n|-\n|align=\"left\"| Austrian Albums Chart<ref>\"[http://austriancharts.at/showitem.asp?interpret=R.E.M.&titel=Monster&cat=a R.E.M. - Monster (Album)] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110921015824/http://austriancharts.at/showitem.asp?interpret=R.E.M.&titel=Monster&cat=a |date=September 21, 2011 }}\". Austriancharts.com (in German). Retrieved on March 19, 2009.</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n|align=\"left\"| Canadian [[RPM (magazine)|''RPM''100]]<ref>\"[http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?&file_num=nlc008388.2640&volume=60&issue=15&issue_dt=October%2031%201994&type=1&interval=24&PHPSESSID=0993221d6a1g58hla2ltbgjme5 RPM100 Albums] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007165758/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?&file_num=nlc008388.2640&volume=60&issue=15&issue_dt=October%2031%201994&type=1&interval=24&PHPSESSID=0993221d6a1g58hla2ltbgjme5 |date=2012-10-07 }}\". ''[[RPM (magazine)|RPM]]'' '''60'''(15). Toronto: RPM Music Publications (October 31, 1994). [[Library and Archives Canada]]. Retrieved on March 20, 2009.</ref>\n| 1\n|-\n|align=\"left\"| [[Hitlisten|Danish Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"Listen\">{{cite news |title=Listen - Danmarks Officielle Hitliste - Udarbejdet af AIM Nielsen for IFPI Danmark - Uge 41 |work=[[Ekstra Bladet]] |location=[[Copenhagen]] |language=Danish |date=1994-10-16 }}</ref>\n| 2\n|-\n|align=\"left\